* Desmonus could see their confusion, but she guessed that she could wait to 
be fed.
Besides, if she could get her claws on that silver bot who had the most 
pleasent smelling mech-fluid she had ever scented before, she could wait.

But then Desmonus brightened her disappointed expression when Reptilica 
finally gave in and said that they could grab a drink after all.
She never failed to notice his hand sliding around her, Bloodystrike doing 
the same, all three bots heading off towards the mass hall.*
